etween 2.6 and 4.4 years of age. Harem males showed a clear decrease in the probability of maintaining social status with age, which suggests that senescence reduces resource holding potential.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Fasel, N.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Saladin, V.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Richner, H.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8e2bb2b38f7e1603b571180e14b9c22c", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/91964afcfcb79eb4defbfad0dc477753ee45bea554564b62b33130ae59ddc7a2", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/S3U4WKHP", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/S3U4WKHP", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/70e263f4dedb9b8665b241650afcb2c4!/b198679-201139", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "11", "pages": "2242-2255", "title": "Journal of Evolutionary Biology", "volume": "29"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8e2bb2b38f7e1603b571180e14b9c22c"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:S3U4WKHP"}, {"identifier": "10.1111/jeb.12949"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid